description: aqi-calculator is an NPM package that allows you to calculate Air Quality Index (AQI) with the help of pollutant concentrations ranging from PM 2.5, PM 10, SO2, NOX, O3 and CO.
name: aqi-calculator

scripts.build: npm run minify && npm run non-minify && npm run config && npm run main
scripts.config: parcel build src/config.js --out-file dist/config.min.js  --no-source-maps --no-cache  --experimental-scope-hoisting  && parcel build src/config.js --out-file dist/config.js --no-minify  --no-source-maps --no-cache  --experimental-scope-hoisting
scripts.main: parcel build src/index.js --out-file dist/index.js  --no-source-maps --no-cache --experimental-scope-hoisting && parcel build src/config.js --out-dir ./  --no-source-maps --no-cache  --experimental-scope-hoisting
